codex
Implemented the V06 fixes and wrote the required report to `.review-slices/V06.fix.md`.

Key changes:
- Added cache hashing via `bundler-packages/bundler-cache/src/cacheHash.js`.
- Cache metadata now includes artifact hash and source file `mtimeMs`, `size`, and content hash.
- Readers verify artifact/source hashes before returning cache hits.
- Artifact writes now happen before metadata writes, with optional atomic rename support.
- Absolute cache dirs are namespaced by project-root hash.
- Bytecode cache validation now requires actual bytecode content.
- Scoped tests were updated to match the new metadata behavior.

Per constraints, I did not run git, package manager, build, or test commands.
